│ The issue is that `icmp slt i32 (sext i16 0), (zext i16 -1)` is different from `icmp slt i16 0, -1` because:                                                                                                   │
│ - sext i16 0 to i32 = 0                                                                                                                                                                                        │
│ - zext i16 -1 (0xFFFF) to i32 = 65535                                                                                                                                                                          │
